Privacy Policy for Limitless Fitness App

Effective Date: 04 November 2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to Limitless Fitness, an application designed to support your fitness goals through tailored workouts, nutritional tracking, and AI-assisted coaching. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use Limitless Fitness, particularly with regard to features like username/password login, Single Sign-On (SSO) and biometric authentication (fingerprint scanning), and AI-powered chatbot interactions.

2. Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: When you create an account, we collect your username, password, and (if applicable) Single Sign-On credentials.
Biometric Data: For security and convenience, we may collect biometric data (e.g., fingerprint scans) if you choose to enable biometric authentication on your device.
Usage Data: Information regarding how you use our app, such as interactions with the chatbot, workout and nutrition logs, and frequency of app usage.
Technical Information: We collect device data (e.g., device type, OS version), IP address, and usage statistics to help improve our appâ€™s functionality and security.
3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

Account Management: To create and manage your account, including username/password and SSO login options.
Authentication and Security: To protect your account, we offer biometric login (fingerprint scanning) and other secure login methods.
AI-Driven Support: Our AI chatbot uses your usage patterns and fitness goals to provide personalized guidance and assistance.
Analytics and Improvement: Usage and technical data help us understand how the app is used, so we can improve features and provide better user experiences.
4. Sharing of Information

Limitless Fitness does not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We may share your data in the following limited situations:

Service Providers: We may work with trusted third parties who assist in app operations, such as hosting and security services. They will only access information needed to perform their tasks and are contractually bound to keep it confidential.
Legal Compliance: If required by law, we may disclose your information to comply with legal obligations, protect our rights, or respond to government requests.
5. Data Security

We use industry-standard security practices, including encryption and secure data storage, to protect your personal information. Biometric data (e.g., fingerprint scans) is stored securely on your device and not transferred to our servers. However, please understand that no system is completely secure. Your account security is also your responsibility, and we recommend using a strong password and enabling two-factor authentication if available.

6. AI Integration and Data Processing

Our AI chatbot processes your data to provide personalized responses. This data is anonymized where possible, and interactions with the AI are stored to improve response accuracy. The AI component respects your privacy, and interactions are only processed within the scope of the app.

7. Retention of Information

We retain your information for as long as needed to provide our services, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.

8. Your Rights and Choices

Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal information, such as the right to access, correct, or delete your data. Please contact us at [contact email] if you wish to exercise any of these rights or have questions about our privacy practices.

9. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or regulatory requirements. We will notify you of any material changes via email or through the app, and your continued use of Limitless Fitness following such updates constitutes acceptance of those changes.

Thank you for choosing Limitless Fitness and trusting us with your information!
